data.description: Price improvement! Tastefully updated two-story, 2-bed, 2-bath condo in the sought-after Timbercove subdivision. This spacious condo lives like a townhome.  One car attached garage! It is an excellent location with easy access to stores, parks, highway 36, schools, and more. Ready for the next owner to move in. Be sure to check out the virtual tour.
